---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 385
  - Title: Aryatârâbhattârikânâmâshtottarasàtakastotra
    Location: 17
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Pilgrimage-Descent Into Hell=Crossing the Flood
Commentary: Amitabha. speaking through Avalokita.
---
When only my names are recollected, I always protect all beings,

I, O Saviour, will ferry them across the great flood of their manifold
fears.
